{"id":205,"parent_id":191,"book_id":95,"content_id":1,"language_id":1,"display_order":205,"title":"3 Nephi 14","subtitle":"","short_title":"3 Ne.","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/3-ne/14","content":[["div",[".titleNumber","Chapter 14"],[".studySummary",["i","Jesus commands: Judge not; ask of God; beware of false prophets—He promises salvation to those who do the will of the Father—Compare",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/matt/7"},"Matthew 7"],". About",["span.small","A.D."],"34."]]],[".bodyBlock",["div",{"id":"1","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/3-ne/14.1","order":"05.22.014.21934"},["b","1"],["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_1a"},"And"],"now it came to pass that when Jesus had spoken these words he turned again to the multitude, and did open his mouth unto them again, saying: Verily, verily, I say unto you, Judge not, that ye be not judged."],["div",{"id":"2","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/3-ne/14.2","order":"05.22.014.21935"},["b","2"],["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_2a"},"For"],"with what judgment ye judge, ye shall be judged; and with what measure ye mete, it shall be measured to you again."],["div",{"id":"3","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/3-ne/14.3","order":"05.22.014.21936"},["b","3"],"And why beholdest thou the mote that is in thy brother’s eye, but considerest not the beam that is in thine own eye?"],["div",{"id":"4","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/3-ne/14.4","order":"05.22.014.21937"},["b","4"],"Or how wilt thou say to thy brother: Let me pull the mote out of thine eye—and behold, a beam is in thine own eye?"],["div",{"id":"5","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/3-ne/14.5","order":"05.22.014.21938"},["b","5"],"Thou",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_5a"},"hypocrite"],", first cast the",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_5b"},"beam"],"out of thine own eye; and then shalt thou see clearly to cast the mote out of thy brother’s eye."],["div",{"id":"6","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/3-ne/14.6","order":"05.22.014.21939"},["b","6"],"Give not that which is",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_6a"},"holy"],"unto the dogs, neither cast ye your pearls before swine, lest they trample them under their feet, and turn again and rend you."],["div",{"id":"7","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/3-ne/14.7","order":"05.22.014.21940"},["b","7"],["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_7a"},"Ask"],", and it shall be given unto you;",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_7b"},"seek"],", and ye shall find; knock, and it shall be opened unto you."],["div",{"id":"8","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/3-ne/14.8","order":"05.22.014.21941"},["b","8"],"For every one that asketh, receiveth; and he that seeketh, findeth; and to him that knocketh, it shall be opened."],["div",{"id":"9","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/3-ne/14.9","order":"05.22.014.21942"},["b","9"],"Or what man is there of you, who, if his son ask bread, will give him a stone?"],["div",{"id":"10","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/3-ne/14.10","order":"05.22.014.21943"},["b","10"],"Or if he ask a fish, will he give him a serpent?"],["div",{"id":"11","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/3-ne/14.11","order":"05.22.014.21944"},["b","11"],"If ye then, being evil, know how to give good gifts unto your children, how much more shall your Father who is in heaven give good things to them that ask him?"],["div",{"id":"12","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/3-ne/14.12","order":"05.22.014.21945"},["b","12"],"Therefore, all things whatsoever ye would that men should do to you,",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_12a"},"do"],"ye even so to them, for this is the law and the prophets."],["div",{"id":"13","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/3-ne/14.13","order":"05.22.014.21946"},["b","13"],"Enter ye in at the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_13a"},"strait gate"],"; for wide is the gate, and",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_13b"},"broad"],"is the way, which leadeth to destruction, and many there be who go in thereat;"],["div",{"id":"14","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/3-ne/14.14","order":"05.22.014.21947"},["b","14"],"Because strait is the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_14a"},"gate"],", and",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_14b"},"narrow"],"is the way, which leadeth unto life, and",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_14c"},"few"],"there be that find it."],["div",{"id":"15","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/3-ne/14.15","order":"05.22.014.21948"},["b","15"],"Beware of",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_15a"},"false prophets"],", who come to you in sheep’s clothing, but inwardly they are ravening wolves."],["div",{"id":"16","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/3-ne/14.16","order":"05.22.014.21949"},["b","16"],"Ye shall know them by their",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_16a"},"fruits"],". Do men gather grapes of thorns, or figs of thistles?"],["div",{"id":"17","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/3-ne/14.17","order":"05.22.014.21950"},["b","17"],"Even so every",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_17a"},"good"],"tree bringeth forth good fruit; but a corrupt tree bringeth forth evil fruit."],["div",{"id":"18","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/3-ne/14.18","order":"05.22.014.21951"},["b","18"],"A good tree cannot bring forth evil fruit, neither a corrupt tree bring forth good fruit."],["div",{"id":"19","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/3-ne/14.19","order":"05.22.014.21952"},["b","19"],"Every tree that",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_19a"},"bringeth"],"not forth good fruit is hewn down, and cast into the fire."],["div",{"id":"20","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/3-ne/14.20","order":"05.22.014.21953"},["b","20"],"Wherefore, by their",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_20a"},"fruits"],"ye shall know them."],["div",{"id":"21","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/3-ne/14.21","order":"05.22.014.21954"},["b","21"],"Not every one that saith unto me, Lord, Lord, shall",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_21a"},"enter"],"into the kingdom of heaven; but he that doeth the will of my Father who is in heaven."],["div",{"id":"22","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/3-ne/14.22","order":"05.22.014.21955"},["b","22"],"Many will",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_22a"},"say"],"to me in that day: Lord, Lord, have we not prophesied in thy name, and in thy name have cast out devils, and in thy name done many wonderful works?"],["div",{"id":"23","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/3-ne/14.23","order":"05.22.014.21956"},["b","23"],"And then will",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_23a"},"I"],"profess unto them: I never",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_23b"},"knew"],"you;",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_23c"},"depart"],"from me, ye that work iniquity."],["div",{"id":"24","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/3-ne/14.24","order":"05.22.014.21957"},["b","24"],"Therefore, whoso heareth these sayings of mine and doeth them, I will liken him unto a wise man, who built his house upon a",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_24a"},"rock"],"—"],["div",{"id":"25","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/3-ne/14.25","order":"05.22.014.21958"},["b","25"],"And the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_25a"},"rain"],"descended, and the floods came, and the winds blew, and beat upon that house; and it",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_25b"},"fell"],"not, for it was founded upon a rock."],["div",{"id":"26","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/3-ne/14.26","order":"05.22.014.21959"},["b","26"],"And every one that heareth these sayings of mine and doeth them not shall be likened unto a",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_26a"},"foolish"],"man, who built his house upon the",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_26b"},"sand"],"—"],["div",{"id":"27","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/3-ne/14.27","order":"05.22.014.21960"},["b","27"],"And the rain descended, and the floods came, and the winds blew, and beat upon that house; and it fell, and great was the fall of it."]]],"refs":[["div",{"id":"1a","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/3-ne/14.1a","order":"05.22.014.21961"},["b","1a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/matt/7.1.1-27"},"Matt. 7:1 (1–27)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/matt/7.1a"},["span.small","JST"],"Matt. 7:1–2 (Matt. 7:1 note",["i","a"],")"],"."],["div",{"id":"2a","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/3-ne/14.2a","order":"05.22.014.21963"},["b","2a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/morm/8.19"},"Morm. 8:19"],"."],["div",{"id":"5a","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/3-ne/14.5a","order":"05.22.014.21965"},["b","5a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/hypocrisy"},"TG Hypocrisy"],"."],["div",{"id":"5b","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/3-ne/14.5b","order":"05.22.014.21967"},["b","5b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/john/8.7.3-11"},"John 8:7 (3–11)"],"."],["div",{"id":"6a","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/3-ne/14.6a","order":"05.22.014.21969"},["b","6a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/holiness"},"TG Holiness"],"."],["div",{"id":"7a","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/3-ne/14.7a","order":"05.22.014.21971"},["b","7a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/3-ne/27.29"},"3 Ne. 27:29"],".",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/prayer"},"TG Prayer"],"."],["div",{"id":"7b","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/3-ne/14.7b","order":"05.22.014.21973"},["b","7b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/initiative"},"TG Initiative"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/objectives"},"Objectives"],"."],["div",{"id":"12a","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/3-ne/14.12a","order":"05.22.014.21975"},["b","12a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/benevolence"},"TG Benevolence"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/compassion"},"Compassion"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/courtesy"},"Courtesy"],"."],["div",{"id":"13a","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/3-ne/14.13a","order":"05.22.014.21977"},["b","13a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/luke/13.24"},"Luke 13:24"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/3-ne/27.33"},"3 Ne. 27:33"],"."],["div",{"id":"13b","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/3-ne/14.13b","order":"05.22.014.21979"},["b","13b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/132.25"},"D&C 132:25"],"."],["div",{"id":"14a","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/3-ne/14.14a","order":"05.22.014.21981"},["b","14a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/9.41"},"2 Ne. 9:41"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/31.9.9,17-18"},"31:9 (9, 17–18)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/22.4"},"D&C 22:4"],"."],["div",{"id":"14b","uri":"/scriptures/bofm/3-ne/14.14b","order":"05.22.014.21983"},["b","14b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"